&lt;Beryllium InternationalCorp> said it has signed a joint venture agreement with ComincoAmerican Inc, a unit of Cominco Ltd &lt;CLT>, to develop aberyllium mine and processing plant on BerylliumInternational's property in the Topaz Mountains southwest ofSalt Lake City.    Beryllium said as a 49 pct owner of the venture iot wouldbe contributing the mine while Cominco, as operator and 51 pctowner, would conduct drilling, metallurgical studies, processtesting and other preliminary work for a feasibility study.    Beryllium said the cost of the preliminary work in 1987,which will start immediately, should be about 250,000 dlrs to300,000 dlrs. Reuter&#3;